  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the efficacy of the investigators PSU hip protector for
      prevention of fracture in elderly.The eligible patients include those with previous diagnosed
      as unilateral hip fracture. They will be randomized into 2 groups;psu hip protector and no
      protector. The patients will be instructed to wear the protector fulltime.The inceidence of
      hip fracture will be compared between both group at the end of 1 year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
